Global Variable# NSMetadataItemFSNameKey

iOS 5.0+iPadOS 5.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.7+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
let NSMetadataItemFSNameKey: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/Foundation/NSMetadataItemFSNameKey#Discussion)

The value is an [`NSString`](/documentation/foundation/nsstring) object with the name of the item as seen in the file system.
